Mirror System:

This works by creating a camera Infront of the mirror and checking what is Infront of the camera. Once we check what's Infront of the camera we take those objects and clone them and then put them inside a viewport frame. We then also add a loop to our function to make the reflection constantly update. The reflections can be adjusted by changing the equation that is used to calculate where the reflection camera will be positioned when the game starts. (edited)
